# Manakish (Lebanese Za'atar Flatbread)

Based on [Holy Cow Vegan](https://holycowvegan.net/manakish-lebanese-flatbread/), [Alphafoodie](https://www.alphafoodie.com/middle-eastern-zaatar-bread-manakish-zaatar/), and [Feel Good Foodie](https://feelgoodfoodie.net/recipe/zaatar-manakeesh/)

